line_1: O with the mighty Theme affected,
line_2: Could I but see thy Head dissected!

line_1: He's ridicul'd for that he but affected.
line_2: And thus his proper road to fame neglected,

line_1: Each Look, each Word, each Smile's affected,
line_2: And inward Charms are quite neglected:

line_1: Whilst to it's sovereign it is well affected,
line_2: For every hive is in itself protected,
